Calling all Ladies of Saigon and beyond ! !
Island_Touch is finaly touching Vietnam ! !
Dont miss the chance to become a part of the largest Bachata family in the World !
When you are a member of a Touch_Team , you will . .
* Receive training in Island_Touch_Bachata style and technique
* Learn choreography by world - renowned Jorge_Burgos & Tanja_Kensinger ( Ataca & La_Alemana )
* Perform at various socials and events
* Have an opportunity to share the stage with Touch_Teams from around the globe at national / international congresses & festivals
* Gain confidence in your social dancing
* Make memories that will last a lifetime and friends that become family
No registration fee
Please arrive 10 minutes earlier to allow registration and warm up .
